snippet.title: Meghan Markle FIGHTS Crew In Leaked Oprah Footage - Part 2
snippet.description:
In this second round of leaked Oprah footage, Meghan Markle continues to fight with one of Oprah's co-host's while the cameras secretly record everything.

In part 2 of this exclusive behind-the-scenes footage, Meghan takes off her gloves and goes head-to-head with one of Oprah's fearless co-hosts. 

The Duchess of Sussex is confronted about the various scandals surrounding her - and it doesn't end well. 

In this 2-minute clip, Meghan Markle claims Kate is a "catty gossip" who "bullies her" and makes her cry. When our co-host calls Meghan out on her B.S. she completely loses it. 

Meghan also drops an unexpected bombshell about her sex life with Harry. 

Let us know what you think about part 2 of this secret Meghan interview in the comments below!
